{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_04_02",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 04 02",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "え？\n明日の最終予選、前乗りしないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?\nYou're not traveling there the day before tomorrow's final qualifying round?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.6911206971853971,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "うん。でも、朝早い便を取ってあるから大丈夫\n二時間前には現地に着いてる予定だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ but I booked an early flight so it's okay.\nI'm scheduled to arrive there two hours early.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.373055565419296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 11.315827894210816
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "そう……いつもは万が一に備えてたのに\nそっちで何かあったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… We usually prepare for the unexpected.\nDid something happen there?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.482494560877484,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "家の事情……って言えばいいのかな\nどうしても私がいないとダメなやつで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess you could say it's a family matter…\nIt's something that absolutely requires me to be there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.949161227544153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 23.749161227544118
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、二時間余裕あれば大丈夫やろうし\n気にせんで大丈夫とちゃう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I guess it'll be okay with two hours to spare.\nDon't worry about it‚ it'll be fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.71582789421082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 29.982494560877516
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "それよりも\n慌てて転んだりせんよう気付けてなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "More importantly‚\nbe careful not to trip and fall in a hurry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.816580339634054,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "子供扱いしないでよ、もう中学三年生なんだから！\nちゃんと余裕持って行動出来るもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't treat me like a kid‚ I'm already in my third year of middle school!\nI can act properly and with plenty of time to spare.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.5524719874064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "……でも……二人とも、ごめんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But… I'm sorry‚ you two.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.08580532073973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 41.08580532073976
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 45.02331104278563
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫、気にしてないわ。お家の事情なんでしょう？\n間に合えば問題ないんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay‚ I'm not worried. It's a family matter‚ right?\nAs long as you're here on time‚ it's not a problem.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.28997770945231,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 51.28997770945235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう\nそれじゃあ、また明日な～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right‚ that's right.\nSee you tomorrow then~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.75664437611899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 54.95664437611896
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "……うん！　それじゃあね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah! See you later!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.956644376118994,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-end-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2066.666666666663,
          "startTime": 57.02331104278566
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 57.55664437611896
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "家の事情……大丈夫かしら\n無理していないといいけれど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Family matters… I wonder if it's okay.\nI hope she's not pushing herself too hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.72331104278565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 62.98997770945237
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃん、お家のことあんまり話さんからなぁ\n一人でいろいろ抱え込んでないか、心配やな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan doesn't talk much about her family.\nI'm worried that she might be shouldering a lot of things on her own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.62331104278563,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 71.72331104278567
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "最終予選が終わったら\nちゃんとみんなで話したいわね、そういうこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After the final qualifying round‚\nwe should all talk properly about things like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.25664437611897,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 76.97438631160281
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "そうやな\nグランプリ優勝に向けて、より結束を固めなあかんし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right.\nWe need to solidify our unity for the Grand Prix victory.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.77438631160283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――グランプリ最終予選、当日の朝",
      "translations": {
        "en": "--The morning of the Grand Prix final qualifying round--",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.4410529782695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 85.24105297826951
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Announcer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-mannouncer001.m4a",
      "text": "東北、北陸を中心に、未明から激しい雨に見舞われ\n交通機関に影響が出ています。気象庁によりますと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Heavy rain has been falling since dawn‚ mainly in the Tohoku and Hokuriku regions‚\naffecting transportation. According to the Japan Meteorological Agency…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.00771964493617,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-end-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7799.999999999997,
          "startTime": 95.7410529782695
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 97.70771964493618
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "……すみれ？\n天気予報見たけど、そっちは大丈夫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sumire?\nI saw the weather forecast‚ is it okay over there?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.70771964493618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとスピード落として運転してるみたい\n風も強いからって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think they're driving a bit slower.\nBecause of the strong wind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.85595287826352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 106.7996392454801
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "でも車内アナウンスだと\nリハには間に合う時間に着くって言ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the announcement on the train said\nwe'll arrive in time for the rehearsal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.26630591214673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 111.28898313503441
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "そう……それなら、私達は先に準備して待ってるわね\n気を付けて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Then we'll get ready and wait for you.\nBe careful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.4223164683678,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　ありがとう\nそれじゃあ、また後でね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay! Thanks!\nSee you later then!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.25105210055177,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-end-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3133.3333333332976,
          "startTime": 121.38438543388507
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫……よね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It'll be alright… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.55105210055176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 121.55105210055177
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 124.9177187672184
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 124.9177187672184
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_02-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "新幹線が止まった！？\n復旧のメドは……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The Shinkansen has stopped!?\nWhat's the estimated time of recovery…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.21771876721849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
